{"tid":1835342,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】墨西哥出現首宗疑似病例　患者為57歲亞裔男子","createTime":"2020-01-22T22:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T01:03:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7afbf12d006b8b5a4f7d09cb8d8a47c4063f17","tid":1835342,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:44:10.000Z","msg":"墨西哥塔毛利帕斯州（Tamaulipas）衛生部周三（22日）表示，當地出現首宗疑似新型冠狀病毒肺炎病例，患者是一名57歲亞裔男子，於去年12月25日前往中國，期間曾停留武漢，現正在接受醫療觀察。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部稱，該名男子住在雷諾薩市（Reynosa），與家人在抵達武漢前，曾到過墨西哥城（Mexico City）、蒂華納（Tijuana）及北京，於本月10日返回墨西哥；上周一（13日）他開始出現咳嗽及流鼻涕等徵狀，疑似帶有新型冠狀病毒，現正在住所接受隔離觀察。<br />\n<br />\nsource:支那01"},{"pid":"3920c3d51ae8bebac85619fe946e93d25aceaa80","tid":1835342,"uid":345470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:49:31.000Z","msg":"全世界攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f6967e15f223fcef0d0bc25efb6d8f7f9c790b","tid":1835342,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:50:07.000Z","msg":"全球股災，由肺炎引發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d682c58f378824c4d9c532862ab6d33e46a28f","tid":1835342,"uid":66365,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:52:04.000Z","msg":"啲dna 泡泡就黎㩒唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94459288c82d36ff1aff777dddf7c4b6083c11c9","tid":1835342,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebe5f9349fca874c22438c0408c3837d5c389cd","tid":1835342,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T22:53:22.000Z","msg":"雖遠必誅"},{"pid":"b87675d0b592f24b